MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: Mapping is to load Onhand data into target BI staging table stg_inventory_Daily
MAPPING.NAME: m_STG_INVENTORY_DAILY

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Source Qualifier to pull Onhand data
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_INVENTORY_DAILY

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT INV.STYLE, INV.COLOR, INV.ATTRIBUTE_CD, INV.SIZE_CD, INV.PLANT_NO, INV.ON_HAND_QTY, INV.MFG_ALLOC_QTY, INV.ON_HOLD_QTY, INV.TOTAL_AVAIL_QTY, INV.CREATE_DATE, INV.UPDATE_DATE, INV.WIP_QTY, INV.TOTAL_ASSIGNED_QTY FROM INVENTORY_DAILY INV JOIN STYLE b on INV.style=b.style_cd join DA.PLANT c on INV.plant_no=c.plant_cd where b.matl_type_cd='00' and c.distribution_ind='Y'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup to get the as_of_Date from day_dimension
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_AS_OF_DATE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select as_of_Date as as_of_Date, 'DUMMY' as DUMMY from day_dimension where day_Date=trunc(sysdate-7)

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT IWE_BRANDS.HARMONIZED_IND as HARMONIZED_IND, IWE_BRANDS.BRAND_CODE as BRAND_CODE FROM IWE_BRANDS IWE_BRANDS

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT IWE_SKU_MASTER.IWE_BRAND as IWE_BRAND, IWE_SKU_MASTER.STYLE_CD as STYLE_CD, IWE_SKU_MASTER.COLOR_CD as COLOR_CD, IWE_SKU_MASTER.ATTRIBUTE_CD as ATTRIBUTE_CD, IWE_SKU_MASTER.SIZE_CD as SIZE_CD FROM IWE_SKU_MASTER IWE_SKU_MASTER

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: STYLE_CD = I_STYLE AND COLOR_CD = I_COLOR AND ATTRIBUTE_CD = I_ATTRIBUTE_CD AND SIZE_CD = I_SIZE_CD
